Image Prompt:
Create an ethereal and majestic depiction of "God Most High" from a Christian perspective. The image should symbolize divine power and sovereignty, portraying a heavenly figure seated on a throne surrounded by radiant light and angelic beings. Include symbolic elements such as a crown, a halo, and heavenly clouds to emphasize the majesty and holiness of God Most High. The setting should evoke a sense of awe and reverence, capturing the transcendent nature of the divine being in a visually captivating manner.
